WEBVTT

00:02:59.258 --> 00:03:04.288
qilish tizimining bakterial tarkibidagi 
farqlar o'rtasidagi aloqani aniqladi.

00:03:04.288 --> 00:03:09.255
Muammo sabablaridan qat'iy nazar, 
semizlik global epidemiyaga aylandi.

00:03:09.255 --> 00:03:12.790
U diabet,

00:03:12.790 --> 00:03:14.136
yurak kasalligi, insult,

00:03:14.136 --> 00:03:15.254
yuqori qon bosimi

00:03:15.254 --> 00:03:16.817
va saraton kabi kasalliklarning

00:03:16.817 --> 00:03:18.322
paydo bo'lish ehtimolini

00:03:18.322 --> 00:03:19.974
sezilarli darajada oshiradi.

00:03:19.974 --> 00:03:24.474
U rivojlangan va rivojlanayotgan 
mamlakatlarda jinsi, yoshi va ijtimoiy

00:03:24.474 --> 00:03:27.512
kelib chiqishidan qat'i nazar,
barchaga ta'sir qilishi mumkin.

00:03:27.512 --> 00:03:32.350
So'nggi 20 yil ichida dunyo bo'ylab
bolalarda semizlik darajasi 60 %ga oshdi,